'''''Beit Yosef''''' ({{lang-he|בית יוסף}}) — also [[Hebrew transliteration|transliterated]] '''''Beth Yosef''''' — is a book by Rabbi [[Joseph Caro]].  It is a long, detailed commentary on the [[Arba'ah Turim]].  It served as a precursor to the ''[[Shulchan Aruch]]'', which Rabbi Caro wrote later in his life.

For more information on this book, see the section [[Shulchan Aruch#Beth Yosef|Beth Yosef]] (in the article [[Shulchan Aruch]]).

